data.title: British Museum
data.meta_description:
Portfolio containing 146 loose prints, with the title printed on the cover, and described on the title-page as '146 Estampas de la Lucha del Pueblo de Mexico: obra colectiva de los artistas del Taller de Grafica Popolar en Mexico', with works by 25 artists; published in an edition of 5,000 in 1960
Containing woodcuts and a few facsimiles of colour lithographs
